### 2. Add Git Pre-commit Hook
Create `.git/hooks/pre-commit`:
```bash
#!/bin/bash
if git diff --cached --name-only | grep -q "^\.env$"; then
    echo "ERROR: Attempting to commit .env file!"
    echo "This file contains secrets and should never be committed."
    exit 1
fi
```

